4️⃣ Troubleshooting & Practical Questions
These test real-world network skills.
• What will you check if internet is not working?
Check cable connection
Check IP address (ipconfig)
Ping gateway
Ping public IP (ping 8.8.8.8)
Check DNS
• ping command
Checks connectivity between devices.
Example:
Copy code

ping google.com
• tracert command
Shows the path a packet takes to reach the destination.
Example:
Copy code

tracert google.com
